1
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:02,000
Gu Haoran.

2
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:07,480
You didn't die from the crash?

3
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:11,120
I'm naturally lucky.

4
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,480
I survived.

5
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:13,800
Ziqing.

6
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:15,880
You are not blind.

7
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:18,380
Why did you find such a piece of trash?

8
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:21,280
Aren't you afraid of losing your own life too?

9
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:24,080
Some people's mouths are like supercar exhausts.

10
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:25,280
They stink.

11
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,130
Chen Ziqing, you...

12
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:30,640
Gu Haoran.

13
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:32,640
Stop making excuses

14
00:01:32,759 --> 00:01:34,090
and trying to save face.

15
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:37,520
The whole city knows now.

16
00:01:38,039 --> 00:01:40,320
Your driving skills are just this.

17
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:41,840
If you ask me,

18
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,900
you should stop driving cars.

19
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:45,770
Go home and drive a tractor.

20
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,520
It's quite comfortable.

21
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:48,530
Isn't it?

22
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:53,080
Today I will, on behalf of Master Gu,

23
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:54,920
teach Ding Wen a lesson.

24
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:56,800
Ding Wen,

25
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:59,360
dare you race me again?

26
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,090
What did you say?

27
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,480
Did I hear that right?

28
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:05,840
My big baby.

29
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,980
You just narrowly escaped death.

30
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:09,759
And you still dare to race me?

31
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,640
Stop talking big.

32
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:14,690
We'll see who's the weakling when someone loses.

33
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:18,280
Can you really do it?

34
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,450
You're asking for death yourself.

35
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,420
Tell me, how do we compete?

36
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:25,810
Let's drift.

37
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,040
Here's the deal.

38
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,770
We each take someone in our car.

39
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:31,240
Whichever of them can't take it first, that person loses.

40
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:31,720
Dare to?

41
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:33,840
Okay.

42
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,840
Then if you lose,

43
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:41,079
run around the 4S dealership naked.

44
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:44,040
Okay.

45
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,480
You are dead meat.

46
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,260
Gu Haoran, can you really do this?

47
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:56,320
Gu Haoran, don't try to be brave.

48
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:58,160
I'll drift for you if you can't.

49
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:58,800
No need.

50
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,480
Dealing with this kind of trash

51
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:02,240
is as easy as stepping on an ant.

52
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:19,000
Ziqing,

53
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:21,900
hold tight when we turn the corner later.

54
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:26,079
You'd better worry about yourself.

55
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:27,440
Gu Haoran.

56
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:30,320
It's not too late for you to back out now.

57
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,050
Cut the crap.

58
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:33,880
You're the one who should be begging for mercy.

59
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:49,600
Kid.

60
00:03:50,079 --> 00:03:51,280
Watch me destroy you.

61
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:54,720
You loser.

62
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:15,520
Gu Haoran.

63
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,770
When did you learn how to drift?

64
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,760
Like I said, I just learned it recently.

65
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,240
How did that loser

66
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:38,240
suddenly get so good at driving?

67
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:40,140
It was just one corner.

68
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:41,880
When it comes to drifting, no one beats you, Mr. Ding.

69
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:43,409
That's true. Hold on tight.

70
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,360
Let's show them what I'm made of.

71
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,880
Gu Haoran, overtake him.

72
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,600
You're not worried about my driving skills anymore?

73
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,800
Since he wants to play,

74
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,460
let's play with him to the end.

75
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,640
Very interesting.

76
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:52,420
Looks like I underestimated this loser.

77
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:57,480
Hang in there.

78
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,680
The final curve is coming up.

79
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,280
Let me show them some tricks.

80
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:03,810
Are you okay?

81
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:05,930
Don't worry.

82
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:07,410
I won't let you lose.

83
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:10,050
Winning or losing doesn't matter.

84
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,340
As long as you're okay,

85
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:12,730
I don't mind streaking.

86
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,560
Thanks for your concern.

87
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:18,480
The next curve is very sharp.

88
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:19,660
Be careful.

89
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:22,560
Got it.

90
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,040
Don't throw up.

91
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:19,840
Hold on.

92
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:22,280
We're almost at the finish line.

93
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,560
You...

94
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,880
When did you learn to drift?

95
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,320
And so fast.

96
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,960
Drifting isn't about speed, it's about stability.

97
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:48,760
Just like you.

98
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,760
You look stubborn on the outside,

99
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,560
but you're steady on the inside.

100
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:55,100
Who said I'm stubborn?

101
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:01,610
Du Mingming.

102
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,380
What the hell did you throw up?

103
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:07,640
Are you crazy?

104
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,800
Do you really think I'm a trash can?

105
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,330
Ding Wen.

106
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:13,400
Taking it out on your girlfriend when you lose.

107
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:14,730
What kind of man are you?

108
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:16,810
What did you say?

109
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:17,720
Who are you?

110
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:19,720
I'm sorry.

111
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,040
I misspoke.

112
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:22,520
I should ask,

113
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,260
are you even human?

114
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,840
Let me tell you something.

115
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,240
I've never been spoken to

116
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:29,740
like this in my whole life.

117
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:30,280
Zhi.

118
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,880
Don't you dare touch her.

119
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,820
So what if I talk about you?

120
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:35,840
Gu Haoran.

121
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,760
Hit me if you dare.

122
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,960
Come on, right here.

123
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:40,760
Come on, hit me.

124
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:41,820
Why would I hit you?

125
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,340
If I really hit you,

126
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,400
our bet for the race would be off.

127
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:50,400
You're just a coward.

128
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,260
Say whatever you want.

129
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:55,580
Anyway, you have to streak in this 4S dealership today.

130
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:56,920
Gu Haoran.

131
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:58,640
Don't go too far.

132
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,480
What?

133
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,740
Are you trying to back out?

134
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:03,410
I recorded a video earlier.

135
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,400
If you back out,

136
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:06,780
I'll post it online

137
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,720
and let everyone see you being a sore loser.

138
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,240
You!

139
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:11,200
Alright.

140
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,330
You can go wash up first.

141
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:20,760
Based on your requirements, ma'am,

142
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:21,480
I recommend this car.

143
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,120
As for this car...

144
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:25,260
It's a new one we imported from Japan.

145
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,000
Oh my god.

146
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:28,680
Holy crap.

147
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:30,520
Right.

148
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:31,920
Coming.

149
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,160
Please wait a moment.

150
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,120
Oh my god.

151
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,400
Honey, look.

152
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:47,960
There's a naked guy here.

153
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:50,560
Don't go.

154
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:04,480
Gu Haoran.

155
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:08,240
How come your driving skills got so good all of a sudden?

156
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,480
It's only been a few days,

157
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,520
but it's like you're a different person.

158
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:13,720
Did this little girl notice something?

159
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,960
I received guidance from a master,

160
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,760
so my driving skills improved by leaps and bounds.

161
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:19,560
Which master?

162
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,660
Ask him to teach me too.

163
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,360
Stop showing off.

164
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,500
Don't move.

165
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,240
It's fine. You keep driving.

166
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,100
I'll pick it up.

167
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:39,920
Oh no.

168
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,820
My ID card is in the wallet.

169
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:43,240
If Ziqing finds out,

170
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,800
my fake identity as Gu Haoran

171
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:45,600
will be completely exposed.
